**********************************************************
* Tivoli Storage Manager Client Configuration            *
**********************************************************
* Puppet Managed Configuration File                      *
* Do not edit this file manually as changes will be      *
* overwritten by the puppetmaster                        *
**********************************************************
* Purpose: Main TSM Client Configuration (dsm.sys)       *
**********************************************************

Servername        <%= tsmserver %>
COMMMethod        TCPip
TCPPort           <%= tsmport || 1500 %>
TCPServeraddress  <%= tsmserver %>
NODENAME          <%= fqdn %>
PASSWORDACCESS    GENERATE
TCPSERVERADDRESS  <%= tsmserver %>

compression       yes

ManagedServices    Schedule
errorlogname /var/log/tsm/dsmerror.log
schedlogname /var/log/tsm/dsmsched.log
errorlogretention 7,D
schedlogretention 7,D

* the order of excludes is important.
inclexcl /opt/tivoli/tsm/client/ba/bin/dsm-linux-exclude.excl
inclexcl /opt/tivoli/tsm/client/ba/bin/dsm-nocompression.excl
